Package com.github.basking2.sdsai.io

Class FileRingOutputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • com.github.basking2.sdsai.io.FileRingOutputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    public class FileRingOutputStream
extends java.io.OutputStream
    A class that reads and writes over a ring of files. When the ring is overwrite pre-existing data, the entire file is truncated and writing restarts. Records written do not span files.
